{
  "stem": "4189.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Every day somebody had to go back to the camp, incidentally.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I had to do it once a week.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "The day that I went to the kitchen, I had to go and bring back the report on how many people were in the factory.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "The factory, incidentally, worked on a 24 hour tour.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We worked from 7 o'clock in the morning until 7 o'clock at night.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And then the next tour came in at 7 o'clock, and worked until 7 o'clock in the morning.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "As one tour walked out, the other tour walked in.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So the factory kept on working around the clock.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "The reason I had to bring back the sheets of the names of people that worked inside the factory was because the-- the camp got paid for every worker that worked in the factory.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We never saw the money, of course.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "We never got the money.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "The SS guards, they got the money-- the one that guarded us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "They got the money.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "They got the payment for us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I don't know how much money it was, but they got paid for every man that worked.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Well, anyway, that particular day, this Max, he wanted to come with me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I said to him-- and this Max, nobody trusted him.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Because we knew that he was too friendly with the meisters.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And he was too friendly with the guards.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "So we did not trust this guy.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "So I was very leery about him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And I told him, right away, I said, look, you cannot come with me, because, look, you don't have a pass.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And if they get caught on the way, you're in trouble.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "They're going to say that you were trying to run away.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he says, I have a pass.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he did.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
